snippet.title: DAILY JOYTIME
snippet.description:
Hey guys! 
My mission is to cheer you up in these weird times we are living in right now ))
I am a single father of one amazing girl, so I really know the importance of creating smile on someone’s face after hard long day )
I want to provide you with the highest quality commentary and I hope you can feel all the effort after watching my videos, because I am doing this full time - I literally spend 8-14 every day on producing my videos and I really love it! ) 

HOW I MAKE MY VIDEOS - I start with research on each topic to find the best way to tell the story in most funny, interesting and entertaining way. Then I edit in Final Cut Pro X studio - I do Cuts, Slow-Motions, Play-backs, Reverse plays and add elements. 
WRITING.. I use DRY english humor and COMMENTATE/REPORT/REACT about all the moments in the videos.
The commentary/editing style is unique and adds value by putting it into my own style.

More details of production process is in the description section of each video ) Cheers!
